summary: All-round diplomat (political affairs incl. peace, security and human rights; development cooperation; cultural, economic and consular affairs), connecting people, themes, files, and sometimes the dots. Enjoys listening, reading, talking and writing. Curious, and privileged to have discovered a lot while realising that there is much more to learn. Likes cinema.
